				<li id="16572622" class="cmnt-root" data="-5" data-d="1648436731000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><a class="comment-username" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&u=139254" rel="nofollow"  target="_blank" style="color: #;">BakedBakerXD</a></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578210/Lightning-Spear" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">27 Mar 2022 23:05</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16572622" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">best way to scale this spell is to have godfreys icon (for when you charge the lightning spear), lightning scorpion charm, flocks canvas talisman, shard of alexander (for main weapon Bolt of gransax. which gives you the upgraded version of the lightning spear called ancient dragon lightning spear. This weapon scales with godfreys icon, lightning scorpion charm, and shard of alexander.) i would scale faith to 65 dex to 40 and strength to 20 the rest of however many levels you wish to spend more of split among mind, vitality, and endurance. for your great rune i would go with morgots rune to gain 5 stat points in all attributes so your faith sits at 70 when your in your world and you have a arc rune popped. next i would set my wonderous physics potion to faith knot and lightning shrouding cracked tear. with all these active your faith should be sitting at 80 when in your world and 75 when in anothers world. to get extra dmg and be more tanky get golden vow and protection of the erdtree. golden vow will also increase your dmg output with lighting spear and bolt of gransax.</p><textarea style="display: