				<li id="16541350" class="cmnt-root" data="13" data-d="1647827304000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578210/Lightning-Spear" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">20 Mar 2022 21:48</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16541350" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">Try and name an incantation which casts as fast, with similar damage, similar range and costs less than 18 fp? The closest ones I can think of are beast claw (smaller range and damage, but costs only 10 fp) and flame of frenzy (small range, but potentially more damage and costs 16 fp). These two spells, however, lack in range and are easily disrupted by terrain. For Lightning spear you can cast it quickly mounted or on foot, with great damage, great range and awesome projectile speed... Of course anyone who wants to be a mage will eventually have to sacrifice some hp flasks for more fp regen, and 18 fp is very fair, considering that there are few incantations that costs less and are practical. One very similar spell is the Frenzied Burst, with a higher cost (33 fp) but even greater reach and damage. The Frenzied Burst, however, seems to cost a bit too much fp to be so spammable. A good strategy it to lure an enemy with the burst until it get in range for the lightning.<br/>The point is: this lightning boi may not have the best damage, nor the best range, but it is above average in almost every parameter and is definetely worth it, as it can be used in almost any situation.</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16541350" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16541350" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">3</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>13</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>0</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16541350"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16541350" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16541350"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
